OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FNew rights to request flexible working
OL,7,Fshould benefit millions of workers,
OL,8,Faccording to workplace experts.
OL,10,FFrom Saturday, employees will have the
OL,11,Flegal right to request flexible
OL,12,Fworking from their first day in a new
OL,13,Fjob.
OL,15,FPreviously it only applied if someone
OL,16,Fhad worked for their employer for 26
OL,17,Fweeks or more.
