OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,F"The pandemic accelerated the
OL,7,Funderstanding of flexible working, and
OL,8,Fthe demand for it, and many
OL,9,Forganisations have responded
OL,10,Fpositively by introducing more
OL,11,Fflexible working policies."
OL,13,FThe conciliation service Acas
OL,14,Fpublished a new statutory Code of
OL,15,FPractice on requests for flexible
OL,16,Fworking alongside guidance.
