OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,F"It sets out good practice on flexible
OL,7,Fworking requests and will help
OL,8,Femployers and employees avoid any
OL,9,Fpitfalls.
OL,11,F"There are many types of flexible
OL,12,Fworking such as part-time working,
OL,13,Fflexitime, job sharing, staggered
OL,14,Fhours, hybrid and homeworking.
OL,16,F"The starting position for businesses
OL,17,Fshould be to consider what may be
OL,18,Fpossible."
