OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,FA study of 4,000 workers by campaign
OL,7,Fgroup Timewise found that half would
OL,8,Fconsider asking for a flexible pattern
OL,9,Fof work using the day one right to
OL,10,Frequest in a new job.
OL,12,FChief executive Claire Campbell said:
OL,13,F"The new legislation will help job
OL,14,Fhunters feel entitled to ask about
OL,15,Fflexible working options and requests
OL,16,Fcould start coming thick and fast.
