OL,3,CNew right to ask for flexible working
OL,4,Cfrom first day in job comes into force
OL,6,F"Flexible working and diversity and
OL,7,Finclusion are interwoven, and
OL,8,Fbusinesses that make the most of the
OL,9,Fopportunity could really open some
OL,10,Fdoors to new and exciting talent."
OL,12,FResearch by campaign group Pregnant
OL,13,FThen Screwed found that mothers are
OL,14,Ftwice as likely as fathers to ask for
OL,15,Fflexible working after parental leave.
